something feels more promising this time around, because it is. 

give yourself time to heal and absorb the fact that things will workout simply because you deserve it. simply because you exist and don’t deserve to feel like you can’t breathe. 

this is your reassurance.

some i feel have a fear of it falling apart. it’s hard to unlearn especially when having previous experiences where stability felt lost. security was scarce. — i promise things are different this time and i know you feel it within.

or trusting that the unknown of something flowing into place doesn’t need to be scary? that there can be reassurance every step of the way but you have to trust. you’re very delicately putting things together in your life.

you deserve to find comfort in those moments where you can just celebrate and achievement or even if it’s finally becoming concrete on a decision.

how flexible have you been to adapting in new environments?

there is a lot of possibility with this pleasure coming your way but you have to remind yourself you’re worthy of it. you’ll be practicing a lot of presence. 

for example, you got the job! enjoy it. celebrate that, don’t move on and forget the milestone.

you’ll be finding many new truths within yourself and taking accountability for things you may have felt annoyed or embarrassed about before. you realize that’s just a part of you that you’ve completely let go of. (or in the process of doing). 

filling your own cup.

all i see is security. there’s a lot you’re establishing in your life right now to be long lasting. a solid relationship, a job, a house/apartment, a project. whatever it is has stability behind it. 

spirit planted the soil and now they’re giving you the rest of the pieces.

you are really balanced when it comes to emotions and thinking logically right now. it wasn’t always like that but you’re finally starting to admire your growth in it’s wholeness. i love that for you. you’re planning for the future whether it’s near or far.

cancer,

you’ve been telling it like it is. — dripping in clear truths. you’re moving proudly and it’s showing. it’s giving you this gloooooww! soon you’ll be receiving a blessing that leads towards more successes. 

pleasure is flying your way.
